annotationA: CG8097, isoform A; ATP binding; arginine-tRNA ligase activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: arginyl-tRNA aminoacylation
annotationB: Serine--tRNA synthetase-like protein Slimp; Essential protein which may play a role in mitochondrial morphogenesis and function. Has transfer RNA (tRNA)-binding activity and can bind tRNA(Ser) but does not have serine--tRNA ligase activity and does not bind ATP
